metadata.name: The Cryptic Game
metadata.description:
The Cryptic Game

Everyone is welcome to play the game. 
But there’s one rule: don’t invest yourself too much in it. 
You'll feel restless with so many inevitable ups and downs alongside its circulating noise. 
With everything in the game that comes with a risk, are you ready to insert the coin?

2022 | 3516 × 4478 px | mp4 | 56 secs

Illustration & animation by Wickana
Audio by DiscoKid909
